data.description: This immaculate & inviting brick home is located on a privacy fenced yard with lovely landscaping. Its light & airy with an open floorplan & large LR with brick fireplace. It also features a well appointed galley kitchen. The split bedroom arrangement allows for a private master suite with spa-like bath. Extras include faux wood blinds throughout + security system, sprinkler system & more. Brokered And Advertised By: Lane Real Estate Services Listing Agent: Roselyn Lane
